{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"革命路上不停留","authors":["丹枫"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":4,"day":13}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命路上不停留"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丹枫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级文化大革命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈火摧枯拉朽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焚烧着积存千年的败"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝腐叶，浊泥污垢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把滋长修正主义的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土壤彻底铲除，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让共产主义大厦的基"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石在伟大的祖国铺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的洪流波涛汹涌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚向前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史的车轮风驰电掣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转动不休；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青的战友们，昂首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阔步朝前进啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万里征途上永不停"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"留！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁说生长在红旗下就"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会迷路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生活中有多少让我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抉择的岔道口！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自然，前进的途中免"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不了摔跤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但跌倒的片刻就应当"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是爬起的时候！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们朝气蓬勃，风华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正茂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不怕电闪雷鸣，风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂雨骤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们是早晨八、九点"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钟的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不能懒懒散散，老"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气横秋！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向头脑中的“私”字猛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烈开火，否则思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会生锈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习“老三篇”，永远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不会有个够！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬起风帆紧跟毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让生命的船驶向霞光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万道的港口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要记住我们是毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想哺育下的年青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤重担压在我们肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快迈步去迎接新的战"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让鲜红的太阳早日照"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍全球！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}